            <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] md:text-sm mb-8 md:mb-12">Начинаем не с любого процесса, а с приоритетного</p>

            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-6 md:p-12 w-full max-w-4xl relative">
                <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-purple-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold uppercase whitespace-nowrap">RUN-процессы — лучшие кандидаты</div>
                
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-12 relative">
                    <!-- Central Node -->
                    <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-48 md:h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-orange-100 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center text-center z-10 shrink-0">
                        <span class="font-black text-sm md:text-xl text-gray-900 leading-tight">Приоритетный<br>процесс</span>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Criteria List -->
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 w-full max-w-md relative z-10">
                        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center gap-3">
                            <i class="ph-fill ph-copy text-purple-500 text-xl shrink-0"></i>
                            <span class="font-bold text-xs md:text-base text-gray-800">Массовые и повторяемые</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center gap-3">
