                    <i class="ph-bold ph-arrow-right text-gray-300 mx-2"></i>
                    <div class="w-[45%] bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 text-[9px] md:text-sm font-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-center">Воркшоп</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 flex flex-row items-center justify-between shadow-sm">
                    <div class="w-[45%] text-[10px] md:text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">Много IT-систем, есть логи</div>
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-arrow-right text-gray-300 mx-2"></i>
                    <div class="w-[45%] bg-white text-gray-700 text-[9px] md:text-sm font-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-center border border-gray-100">Анализ интерфейсов / Process mining</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 flex flex-row items-center justify-between shadow-sm">
                    <div class="w-[45%] text-[10px] md:text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">Нужно убедить руководство</div>
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-arrow-right text-gray-300 mx-2"></i>
                    <div class="w-[45%] bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 text-[9px] md:text-sm font-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-center">Benchmarking</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 flex flex-row items-center justify-between shadow-sm">
                    <div class="w-[45%] text-[10px] md:text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">Нужно структурировать сложные знания</div>
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-arrow-right text-gray-300 mx-2"></i>
                    <div class="w-[45%] bg-white text-gray-700 text-[9px] md:text-sm font-bold px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-center border border-gray-100">Mind map и анализ правил</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center text-[9px] md:text-sm text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
