                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-git-branch text-2xl text-purple-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <span class="font-bold text-[9px] md:text-sm text-gray-800">4. Модель AS-IS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-full hover:border-purple-300">
                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-crosshair text-2xl text-purple-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <span class="font-bold text-[9px] md:text-sm text-gray-800">5. Карта точек автоматизации</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-full hover:border-orange-300">
                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-git-merge text-2xl text-orange-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <span class="font-bold text-[9px] md:text-sm text-gray-800">6. Модель TO-BE</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-full hover:border-orange-300">
                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-user-switch text-2xl text-orange-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <span class="font-bold text-[9px] md:text-sm text-gray-800">7. Новая роль человека</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-full hover:border-orange-300">
                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-graph text-2xl text-orange-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <span class="font-bold text-[9px] md:text-sm text-gray-800">8. Граф навыков агента</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-full hover:border-orange-300">
                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-chart-bar text-2xl text-orange-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <span class="font-bold text-[9px] md:text-sm text-gray-800">9. Метрики пилота</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-3 md:p-4 shadow-sm flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-full hover:border-orange-300">
                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-calendar text-2xl text-orange-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <span class="font-bold text-[9px] md:text-sm text-gray-800">10. План внедрения</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center font-bold text-[10px] md:text-sm text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 py-3 rounded-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto border border-gray-200">
                Проект автоматизации начинается не с кода, а с <span class="text-purple-600">проектного пакета</span>.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- СЛАЙД 31: Дальнейшие шаги (Roadmap) -->
    <div class="slide-container px-2 md:px-12 opacity-0 pointer-events-none translate-y-8" id="slide-30">
        <div class="content-z max-w-6xl">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-2 text-center text-gray-900">Дальнейшие <span class="gradient-text">шаги</span></h2>
            <p class="text-center text-gray-500 font-bold text-[10px] md:text-sm mb-12 md:mb-20">AgentOps превращает автоматизацию в управляемый процесс</p>
            
            <div class="relative w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <!-- Line -->
                <div class="absolute top-[30px] md:top-[40px] left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gray-200 z-0"></div>
                <div class="absolute top-[30px] md:top-[40px] left-0 w-[16%] h-1 bg-purple-500 z-0"></div> <!-- Progress line -->
                
                <div class="flex flex-row justify-between relative z-10 w-full px-2">
                    <!-- Step 1 -->
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-1/6">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-20 md:h-20 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-purple-500 shadow-sm relative mb-2">
                            <i class="ph-bold ph-map-trifold text-xl md:text-3xl"></i>
                            <div class="absolute -top-2 md:-top-3 bg-purple-500 text-white text-[6px] md:text-[10px] px-1.5 md:px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold whitespace-nowrap">В процессе</div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-[7px] md:text-xs font-bold text-gray-800 text-center leading-tight">Понимание бизнеса</span>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Step 2 -->
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-1/6">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-20 md:h-20 bg-white border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 shadow-md mb-2 md:transform md:-translate-y-2 transition-transform">
                            <i class="ph-fill ph-code text-xl md:text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-[7px] md:text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 text-center leading-tight">Разработка агента</span>
