                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-shield-check text-2xl text-purple-500 shrink-0"></i>
                    <span class="text-[10px] md:text-sm font-bold text-gray-800 leading-tight">Управление и безопасность</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center gap-3">
                    <i class="ph-duotone ph-warning text-2xl text-orange-500 shrink-0"></i>
                    <span class="text-[10px] md:text-sm font-bold text-gray-800 leading-tight">Нестабильный процесс</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-4 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center gap-3">
